episodes.title: Kendra Petty, Executive Vice President, Community Forum with Suze Shaner, 7/11/23
episodes.description: Suze Shaner interviews Kendra Petty, an Executive Vice President of a transportation, parking and real estate company, and also a survivor of Trauma. They discuss Kendra's debut memoir, I Can't Believe Believe I'm Not Dead: Escaping abuse, a cult, attempted murder, and other insanities...a story that cannot be true, but is. Suze and Kendra explore how she was able to heal from trauma and what advice she would give to others in abusive situations. You may reach Kendra at: http://kendrapettyofficial.com/
